<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Pinch — March 2026 Performance Recap</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #0f0f0f;
    --paper: #f5f2ed;
    --gold: #b8932a;
    --gold-light: #d4aa4a;
    --slate: #2c3340;
    --slate-mid: #4a5568;
    --slate-light: #8896aa;
    --danger: #c0392b;
    --success: #1a6b45;
    --warning: #b8590a;
    --rule: #d8d2c8;
    --card-bg: #ffffff;
    --highlight: rgba(184,147,42,0.08);
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  .masthead {
    background: var(--slate);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 56px 64px 48px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .masthead::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; right: 0;
    width: 340px; height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 40%, rgba(184,147,42,0.12) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .masthead-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .masthead h1 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 58px;
    font-weight: 300;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .masthead h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }
  .masthead-sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .masthead-rule {
    width: 48px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin: 24px 0;
  }
  .masthead-tagline {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 17px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    max-width: 540px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .container {
    max-width: 1060px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 48px;
  }

  section {
    padding: 56px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
  }
  section:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.24em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 32px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--slate);
  }

  /* ── EXECUTIVE SUMMARY ── */
  .exec-summary {
    background: var(--slate);
    color: white;
    padding: 40px 48px;
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .exec-summary::after {
    content: '"';
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 220px;
    line-height: 1;
    color: rgba(184,147,42,0.08);
    position: absolute;
    right: 30px;
    top: -20px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .exec-summary p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.85;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
    max-width: 760px;
  }
  .exec-summary p + p { margin-top: 14px; }
  .exec-summary strong { color: var(--gold-light); font-weight: 500; }

  /* ── KPI CARDS ── */
  .kpi-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
    margin: 28px 0;
  }
  .kpi-grid-2 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
  }
  .kpi-grid-4 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
  }
  .kpi-grid-5 {
    grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
  }

  .kpi {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 22px 24px 20px;
    position: relative;
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .kpi:hover { box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.07); }
  .kpi-label {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--slate-light);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .kpi-value {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 38px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--slate);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .kpi-value.sm { font-size: 28px; }
  .kpi-vs { font-size: 11px; color: var(--slate-light); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .kpi-delta { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; }
  .delta-up { color: var(--success); }
  .delta-down { color: var(--danger); }
  .delta-warn { color: var(--warning); }
  .kpi-note { font-size: 10.5px; color: var(--slate-light); margin-top: 8px; line-height: 1.5; }

  .kpi.featured {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--slate) 0%, #1e2940 100%);
    border-color: transparent;
    color: white;
  }
  .kpi.featured .kpi-label { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); }
  .kpi.featured .kpi-value { color: white; }
  .kpi.featured .kpi-vs { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }

  .kpi.gold-accent { border-top: 2px solid var(--gold); }
  .kpi.danger-accent { border-top: 2px solid var(--danger); }
  .kpi.success-accent { border-top: 2px solid var(--success); }

  /* ── FLAG BADGES ── */
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-left: 6px;
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
  .badge-red { background: #fdf0ef; color: var(--danger); border: 1px solid rgba(192,57,43,0.2); }
  .badge-green { background: #edf7f2; color: var(--success); border: 1px solid rgba(26,107,69,0.2); }
  .badge-gold { background: rgba(184,147,42,0.1); color: var(--gold); border: 1px solid rgba(184,147,42,0.3); }
  .badge-warn { background: #fdf5ef; color: var(--warning); border: 1px solid rgba(184,89,10,0.2); }

  /* ── TABLES ── */
  .data-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }
  .data-table th {
    font-size: 9.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--slate-light);
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    text-align: left;
    background: #fafaf8;
  }
  .data-table th.right { text-align: right; }
  .data-table td {
    padding: 11px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ece6;
    color: var(--slate);
  }
  .data-table td.right { text-align: right; }
  .data-table td.bold { font-weight: 500; }
  .data-table tr:hover td { background: var(--highlight); }
  .data-table tr.total-row td {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    background: #fafaf8;
  }
  .data-table tr.highlight-row td {
    background: rgba(184,147,42,0.06);
  }
  .table-wrapper {
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* ── TEXT CONTENT ── */
  .insight-block {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 32px;
    margin: 24px 0;
  }

  .insight-card {
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 24px;
  }
  .insight-card h4 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--slate);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .insight-card p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--slate-mid);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .insight-card p + p { margin-top: 10px; }
  .insight-card.alert {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--danger);
    background: #fdfcfc;
  }
  .insight-card.opportunity {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--success);
    background: #fcfdfb;
  }
  .insight-card.caution {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--warning);
    background: #fdfcfb;
  }

  .prose {
    font-size: 13.5px;
    color: var(--slate-mid);
    line-height: 1.85;
    max-width: 820px;
  }
  .prose strong { color: var(--slate); font-weight: 500; }
  .prose + .prose { margin-top: 14px; }

  /* ── PRIORITY LIST ── */
  .priority-list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 20px 0;
  }
  .priority-list li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 18px 20px;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--slate-mid);
  }
  .priority-list li strong { color: var(--slate); font-weight: 500; display: block; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .priority-num {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 28px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .priority-list li.critical { border-left: 3px solid var(--danger); }
  .priority-list li.important { border-left: 3px solid var(--warning); }
  .priority-list li.strategic { border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); }

  /* ── DIVIDER ── */
  .divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--rule);
    margin: 28px 0;
  }

  /* ── CHANNEL BAR ── */
  .channel-bar-wrap { margin: 10px 0 4px; }
  .channel-bar {
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    background: var(--rule);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
  }
  .channel-bar-fill { height: 100%; border-radius: 2px; transition: width 0.6s ease; }
  .bar-direct { background: #2c3f6b; }
  .bar-organic { background: #4a8c6e; }
  .bar-email { background: #007bbf; }
  .bar-paid { background: #6b4fc8; }
  .bar-referral { background: #b87333; }

  /* ── CALLOUT BOX ── */
  .callout {
    border: 1px solid var(--gold);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--gold);
    background: rgba(184,147,42,0.05);
    border-radius: 3px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--slate);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
  .callout strong { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; }

  .callout-danger {
    border-color: var(--danger);
    border-left-color: var(--danger);
    background: rgba(192,57,43,0.04);
  }
  .callout-danger strong { color: var(--danger); }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: var(--slate);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    padding: 32px 64px;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  footer strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); }

  /* ── TWO COL ── */
  .two-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .three-col {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 800px) {
    .masthead { padding: 40px 28px; }
    .masthead h1 { font-size: 40px; }
    .container { padding: 0 24px; }
    .kpi-grid, .kpi-grid-4, .kpi-grid-5 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .two-col, .insight-block, .three-col { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- MASTHEAD -->
<div class="masthead">
  <div class="masthead-eyebrow">Confidential · Monthly Performance Report</div>
  <h1>The <em>Pinch</em></h1>
  <p class="masthead-sub">March 2026 &nbsp;·&nbsp; Charleston, South Carolina</p>
  <div class="masthead-rule"></div>
  <p class="masthead-tagline">A strong revenue month defined by ADR leadership and OTA growth — clouded by a PPC structure that urgently requires intervention and a loyalty segment in significant decline.</p>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <!-- EXECUTIVE SUMMARY -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-label">Executive Summary</div>
    <div class="section-title">The View from 30,000 Feet</div>

    <div class="exec-summary">
      <p>March 2026 delivered a <strong>$444,055 in room revenue</strong> — up <strong>+9% year-over-year</strong> — driven by meaningful ADR growth of $42 per night and a modest 12-night volume increase. The Pinch continues to dominate its competitive set with a RevPAR Index of <strong>142.4</strong>, comfortably above target, and ranks #2 of 5 in its comp set at a $653 ADR that is $126 ahead of the set average.</p>
      <p>However, this strong top-line performance carries important caveats. <strong>Loyalty segment volume collapsed by 64%</strong> (−57 room nights), organic web revenue fell 26%, and the PPC program earned an <strong>F grade</strong> — with 75% of ad spend allocated to brand terms against a target of ≤18%. The website's overall conversion rate declined 14.8% year-over-year even as traffic grew 27%. Email marketing emerged as the month's most efficient channel, converting at 3.8% and generating $32.8K from fewer than 450 sessions. These signals — both the wins and the warnings — demand attention entering the high-demand spring shoulder season.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- HEADLINE METRICS -->
    <div class="kpi-grid kpi-grid-4">
      <div class="kpi featured">
        <div class="kpi-label">Total Room Revenue</div>
        <div class="kpi-value">$444K</div>
        <div class="kpi-vs">vs $407K · Mar 2025</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta delta-up">↑ +$36,712 &nbsp;(+9.0%)</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi gold-accent">
        <div class="kpi-label">ADR</div>
        <div class="kpi-value">$637</div>
        <div class="kpi-vs">vs $595 · Mar 2025</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta delta-up">↑ +$42 &nbsp;(+7.1%)</div>
        <div class="kpi-note">$126 above comp set average</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi gold-accent">
        <div class="kpi-label">Room Nights Sold</div>
        <div class="kpi-value">697</div>
        <div class="kpi-vs">vs 685 · Mar 2025</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta delta-up">↑ +12 nights</div>
      </div>
      <div class="kpi gold-accent">
        <div class="kpi-label">RevPAR Index</div>
        <div class="kpi-value">142.4</div>
        <div class="kpi-vs">vs 139.8 · Mar 2025</div>
        <div class="kpi-delta delta-up">↑ +2.6 pts &nbsp;· Above Target</div>
        <div class="kpi-note">Target ≥ 115.0</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- REVENUE MANAGEMENT -->
  <section>
    <div class="section-label">Revenue Management</div>
    <div class="section-title">Competitive Position & Segment Analysis</div>

    <div class="prose">The Pinch continues to command a significant rate premium over its competitive set — a testament to the property's positioning and consistent pricing discipline. Despite a slight occupancy dip (-1.2 percentage points year-over-year), RevPAR grew 8.6% to $571, substantially outpacing the comp set's 6.6% gain. The RevPAR index improved by 2.6 points. The one concern: market share penetration fell 5.2% and the property dropped from <strong>rank #1 to #2</strong> in its competitive set — primarily reflecting the comp set gaining occupancy at a faster rate.</div>

    <div class="section-title" style="font-size:22px; margin-top:32px;">STR Performance vs. Competitive Set</div>

    <div class="table-wrapper">
      <table class="data-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Metric</th>
            <th class="right">The Pinch — Mar 2026</th>
            <th class="right">The Pinch — Mar 2025</th>
            <th class="right">Change</th>
            <th class="right">Comp Set — Mar 2026</th>
            <th class="right">Comp Set Change</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="bold">Occupancy</td>
            <td class="right">87.4%</td>
            <td class="right">88.5%</td>
            <td class="right"><span class="kpi-delta delta-warn">↓ −1.2%</span></td>
