          The Pinch slipped from #1 to #2 in RevPAR ranking within its competitive set, with market share penetration falling 5.2%. While ADR leadership is secure and RevPAR index remains above target, the comp set is gaining occupancy ground faster. Ensure April–June pace targets account for comp set recovery. Consider tactical promotions for mid-week and value-season dates to rebuild occupancy index advantage.
